snippet.title: Afandas Survival - Open World Survival Game - Upcoming Game 2018
snippet.description:
Afandas Survival is an open world survival game. After a plague wipes out most of the population, you're one of the few survivors on an island called Afanda.

Steam Store:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/792750/Afandas_Survival/
